{"tid":1470562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"睇咗成朝新聞， 主流言論都未放棄連登仔，我哋憑咩放棄自己","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:18:18.000Z","uid":135867,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6832116abc9e257347dc205c407c5b411697cc99","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"根本而家全個社會都憎政府同埋警察<br />\n我哋如果因為小小挫折就鬧交鬧到咁樣<br />\n係非常之唔值得<br />\n睇咗記協個聲明，立場篇文， 根本主流言論都未放棄我哋<br />\n我哋啲嘢時間應該做嘅係睇下之後有咩可以做<br />\n<br />\n我哋只係一班普通市民<br />\n做錯嘢係好正常嘅事<br />\n意見唔同都係好正常嘅事<br />\n但係我哋有到好處就係進化得好快<br />\n<br />\n政府而家就係要以快打慢 唔可以畀你班人 有時間 諗同埋進化<br />\n<br />\n我哋真係冇時間同冇本錢再同任何人割蓆同埋捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n總之要做嘅嘢就做咗先<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"ae2d17818445c47aa080a0726e8d66c0b5590d0d","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a025c175de1edfd183aca053b37b93d966f73378","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e27d807f880c880aa227bf6e6efde6d1e73ae12","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f3bce0bfe5ddb5ad41ef4abd136b29b5bfae5f","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1874678e2e6bf49cac174eb09425226f05c8cd2e","tid":1470562,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48650d03db5facc2ff0ed5837d8ba4a803ba62cd","tid":1470562,"uid":164374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14