,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，停手呀，失民意啦失民意啦，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n係咪真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效得黎，<br />\n而又乜人都影響唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話民意完全無用，<br />\n一黎民意早已經歸曬邊唔會轉，中立花生友要黎都廢，<br />\n二黎香港又唔係民主政府，幾時有理過民意，<br />\n仲想單靠攬住民意過世? <br />\n文宣到有700萬人一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫手打政府? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人救過死左好多人嘅烏克蘭、蘇丹、新疆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋有民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n唔好本末倒置，因為民意勒索而乜都唔敢做，<br />\n首要目的係要贏，<br />\n民意至上主義係好，不過等有左民主政府先講啦，<br />\n各有各做，出核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"456fd1da2ad253588f0198cfddf6bbfc60cd106f","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d436b2e92f954e09201984a98ed8c334bd1edf43","tid":1470562,"uid":188432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f30115fecce91fbc7e3d65d66cc367c7c0f70049","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5297b7dbe1a444385ee157633d903c281388609f","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4a334ee14b42a8802e152c4c02a9fc4a952a70","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c508c99062d466c660bab765c49b0a55fd1cdd","tid":1470562,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl